e/Emmanuelle\"}, {\"begin\": 738, \"end\": 742, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ernst_Witt\", \"score\": 0.9979906484554129, \"rank\": 0.0019369324619405936, \"text\": \"Witt\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ernst_Witt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ernst_Witt\"}, {\"begin\": 819, \"end\": 823, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alma_Mahler\", \"score\": 0.9996460783899636, \"rank\": 0.00027586223799666224, \"text\": \"Alma\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alma_Mahler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alma_Mahler\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a 35-year-old communications freelancer\", \"from\": 743, \"to\": 782}, {\"ngram\": \"police\", \"from\": 802, \"to\": 808}, {\"ngram\": \"town\", \"from\": 850, \"to\": 854}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She desperately went on her phone to fill out the online form to get her QR code, unaware that the vetting process could take several days.\", \"from\": 857, \"to\": 996, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her phone\", \"from\": 881, \"to\": 890}, {\"ngram\": \"the online form\", \"from\": 903, \"to\": 918}, {\"ngram\": \"her QR code\", \"from\": 926, \"to\": 937}, {\"ngram\": \"the vetting process\", \"from\": 952, \"to\": 971}, {\"ngram\": \"several days\", \"from\": 983, \"to\": 995}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Those with the precious code - either on their phones or printed out on pieces of paper - passed smoothly past police checkpoints at gaps in the barriers taller than most people.\", \"from\": 998, \"to\": 1176, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the precious code\", \"from\": 1009, \"to\": 1026}, {\"ngram\": \"their phones\", \"from\": 1039, \"to\": 1051}, {\"ngram\": \"pieces\", \"from\": 1070, \"to\": 1076}, {\"ngram\": \"paper\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1085}, {\"ngram\": \"police checkpoints\", \"from\": 1109, \"to\": 1127}, {\"ngram\": \"gaps\", \"from\": 1131, \"to\": 1135}, {\"ngram\": \"the barriers\", \"from\": 1139, \"to\": 1151}, {\"ngram\": \"most people\", \"from\": 1164, \"to\": 1175}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Those without got mostly got turned away - with no amount of grumbling and cajoling making officers budge.\", \"from\": 1178, \"to\": 1284, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no amount\", \"from\": 1226, \"to\": 1235}, {\"ngram\": \"officers\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1277}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's too much, that's over the top, that whole thing is a pain,\\\" grumbled Nassim Bennamou, a delivery man who was denied access to the street leading to Notre Dame Cathedral on his scooter.\", \"from\": 1286, \"to\": 1478, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the top\", \"from\": 1316, \"to\": 1323}, {\"ngram\": \"that whole thing\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1341}, {\"ngram\": \"a pain\", \"from\": 1345, \"to\": 1351}, {\"ngram\": \"Nassim Bennamou\", \"from\": 1363, \"to\": 1378}, {\"ngram\": \"a delivery man\", \"from\": 1380, \"to\": 1394}, {\"ngram\": \"access\", \"from\": 1410, \"to\": 1416}, {\"ngram\": \"the street\", \"from\": 1420, \"to\": 1430}, {\"ngram\": \"Notre Dame Cathedral\", \"from\": 1442, \"to\": 1462}, {\"ngram\": \"his scooter\", \"from\": 1466, \"to\": 1477}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Even the GPS is confused, I have no idea how I am going to work today,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 1480, \"to\": 1562, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Even the GPS\", \"from\": 1481, \"to\": 1493}, {\"ngram\": \"no idea\", \"from\": 1514, \"to\": 1521}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While authorities announced the code system last year and have been meeting with local residents for months to explain the restrictions, not everyone was aware.\", \"from\": 1566, \"to\": 1726, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"authorities\", \"from\": 1572, \"to\": 1583}, {\"ngram\": \"the code system\", \"from\": 1594, \"to\": 1609}, {\"ngram\": \"local residents\", \"from\": 1647, \"to\": 1662}, {\"ngram\": \"months\", \"from\": 1667, \"to\": 1673}, {\"ngram\": \"the restrictions\", \"from\": 1685, \"to\": 1701}, {\"ngram\": \"not everyone\", \"from\": 1703, \"to\": 1715}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many visitors were redirected to reach Paris' most iconic monuments.\", \"from\": 1727, \"to\": 1795, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1766, \"end\": 1771, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.209493718995659e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Many visitors\", \"from\": 1727, \"to\": 1740}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We had no idea we needed a QR code,\\\" said Takao Sakamoto, 55, who was denied access to theEiffel Towernear the Bir Hakeim metro station.\", \"from\": 1797, \"to\": 1934, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1840, \"end\": 1854, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Takao_Sakamoto\", \"score\": 0.9999998026910556, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Takao Sakamoto\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Takao_Sakamoto\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Takao_Sakamoto\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no idea\", \"from\": 1805, \"to\": 1812}, {\"ngram\": \"a QR code\", \"from\": 1823, \"to\": 1832}, {\"ngram\": \"access\", \"from\": 1875, \"to\": 1881}, {\"ngram\": \"theEiffel Towernear\", \"from\": 1885, \"to\": 1904}, {\"ngram\": \"the Bir Hakeim metro station\", \"from\": 1905, \"to\": 1933}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Visiting from Japan with his wife, he took a photo of the Eiffel Tower from a distance, behind the fences and police cars.\", \"from\": 1935, \"to\": 2057, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Japan\", \"from\": 1949, \"to\": 1954}, {\"ngram\": \"his wife\", \"from\": 1960, \"to\": 1968}, {\"ngram\": \"a photo\", \"from\": 1978, \"to\": 1985}, {\"ngram\": \"the Eiff